  "remarks": "\nNariman Gadzhievich \nGADZHIEV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because GADZHIEV is associated with a person who is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, namely Suleyman Abusaidovich KERIMOV.  \n",
